With a slightly worn-in façade, complete with a matte finish, this 6” hexagon tile will make a splash in any space it’s placed. Hailing from Spain, these porcelain tiles can be used on walls or floors. About The Collection: Gorgeous, encaustic look porcelain tiles from Spain make up the Sasha Hex Collection.
